---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import ProfileCard from "../components/ProfileCard.astro";
---
<Base title="Aditya Wagh">
  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="mb-6 md:float-left md:mr-8 md:mb-3 md:mt-2">
      <ProfileCard />
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-center">Hi, I'm Aditya Wagh</h1>

      <p>
        I'm a Research Engineer at <a href="https://neuracore.com">Neuracore</a>, a company founded by
        <a href="https://stepjam.github.io/">Stephen James</a>, where I build physical-AI infrastructure for robot
        learning. I'm extremely grateful to be educated at two great institutions:
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_University">NYU</a> and
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BITS_Pilani">BITS Pilani</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        My interests span computer vision, robot learning, and world models.
      </p>

      <p>
        Earlier, I worked on Point Cloud Representation Learning and Simultaneous Localization and Mapping (SLAM) at
        NYU's <a href="https://ai4ce.github.io/">AI4CE lab</a> under Professor
        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&user=YeG8ZM0AAAAJ">Chen Feng</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm always open to research collaborations and roles in world models, computer vision, and autonomy.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside work, I'm into coding agents and AR/XR, and I read across programming languages, systems and
        performance engineering, ML systems, and topics like public policy, history, and psychology.
      </p>

      <p>
        If any of this resonates, let's connect — reach me on
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adityamwagh">LinkedIn</a>, by
        <a href="mailto:adityamwagh@outlook.com">email</a>, or on
        <a href="https://twitter.com/adityamwagh">X/Twitter</a> (open DMs).
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="clear-both"></div>
  </section>
</Base>
